Weekend and Independence Day of Kobi Shimoni, Subliminal
What does your typical Friday look like?
Weekends are the most important days of my life.
Faith and tradition are deep in my heart.
My Fridays are dedicated to children, Or (10) and Jonathan (8).
I pick them up from school, we buy flowers and groceries for Kiddush, have lunch and do something fun together, like play football, ride horses or play with cars on a sign.
