A model for healing: Three senior doctors tell of their mentors
Prof. Galia Rahav misses the wit and wisdom of the late Prof. Marvin Shapira, especially during the pandemic •
Dr. Shlomi Kodesh does not forget, even from the height of his position, the push from the late Prof. Shaul Soknik •
