A senior police official: "Government policy and setting goals are required here"
The Israeli police have launched an operation to eradicate the phenomenon of illegal residents, but the road is still long.
There is no single factor in the State of Israel today that encompasses this entire issue. "
"If we want to address the phenomenon of illegal residents, a government policy is required, and from it we must derive goals, tasks and responsibilities.
